    "feat": {
        "name": "Basic Skysage Divination",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "The stars move, granting you a sliver of their magic. Choose one of the following 1st-rank spells to your spell repertoire: *object reading* or *sure strike*. You can Cast this Spell as an occult Oatia skysage spell.  \n  \nAt 6th level, choose one of the following 2nd-rank spells to add to your spell repertoire: *augury* or *see the unseen*. At 8th level, you choose one of the following 3rd-rank spells to add to your spell repertoire: *clairaudience* or *locate*.",
